This paper deals with updates in RDF stores and entailment regimes, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses potential strategies for implementing the semantics, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper focuses on a fragment of SPARQL corresponding to DL-Lite, which is a description logic (cs.DL).
